      "line": 29,
      "text": "FUNCTION"
    },
    {
      "line": 32,
      "text": "The WHOLE EARTH CATALOG functions as an evaluation and access"
    },
    {
      "line": 35,
      "text": "device. With it, the user should know better what is worth getting and"
    },
    {
      "line": 36,
      "text": "where and how to do the getting."
    },
    {
      "line": 39,
      "text": "An item is listed in the CATALOG if it is deemed:"
    },
    {
      "line": 40,
      "text": "1) Useful as a tool,"
    },
    {
      "line": 43,
      "text": "2) Relevant to independent education,"
    },
    {
      "line": 44,
      "text": "3) High quality or low cost,"
    },
    {
      "line": 45,
      "text": "4) Easily available by mail."
    },
    {
      "line": 48,
      "text": "CATALOG listings are continually revised according to the experience"
    },
    {
      "line": 49,
      "text": "and suggestions of CATALOG users and staff."
    },
    {
      "line": 52,
      "text": "PURPOSE"
    },
    {
      "line": 55,
      "text": "We are as gods and might as well get good at it. So far remotely done"
    },
    {
      "line": 56,
      "text": "power and glory--as via government, big business, formal education,"
    },
    {
      "line": 57,
      "text": "church--has succeeded to point where gross defects obscure actual"
    },
    {
      "line": 58,
      "text": "gains. In response to this dilemma and to these gains a realm of intimate,"
    },
    {
      "line": 59,
      "text": "personal power is developing--power of the individual to conduct his"
    },
    {
      "line": 60,
      "text": "own education, find his own inspiration, shape his own environment, and"
    },
    {
      "line": 61,
      "text": "share his adventure with whoever"
    },
    {
      "line": 62,
      "text": "process are sought and promoted by the WHOLE EARTH CATALOG."
